attributes.body: Modified Grapes is an Indica weed strain resulting from a cross between GMO and Purple Punch. According to our customers, Modified Grapes is associated with effects like drowsiness, relaxation, and arousal. Consumers often turn to Modified Grapes to alleviate symptoms related to anxiety, stress, and insomnia.

Enchanted Botanicals - Orange Punch
attributes.body: Orange Punch is a Sativa cannabis strain known for its extremely citrusy aroma and flavor, reminiscent of oranges. Our particular Orange Punch is a cross between Purple Punch and Mandarin Cookies. It delivers balanced effects despite being a sativa, providing calm relaxation and euphoria in both the body and the mind. Our customers have reported some therapeutic benefits, including stress relief and mood enhancement.

attributes.name: Enchanted Botanicals - Concord Cream
attributes.body: Concord Cream, a predominantly Indica strain, is the sweet sweet love child of Grape Bubba and Cookies & Cream. This soothing bud, rich in flavor, is a must-try for any grape strain fans. True to its name, Concord Cream boasts a super sweet and creamy fruity grape flavor complemented by notes of flowery violet and vanilla. The aroma mirrors this profile with a hint of sour grapefruit. Concord Cream is a favored choice for addressing various conditions across a whole spectrum, including stress, anxiety, muscle spasms, cramps, depression, and insomnia. The Concord Cream high unfolds gradually, initiating with a slow burn of euphoria that melts the mad/sad away. Concord Cream is wonderful for consumers that have social anxiety as its a very talkative, giggly strain! As the mental boost persists, a sense of physical relaxation takes over, eventually inducing a sleepy, sedative state.

Enchanted Botanicals - Peach Crescendo
attributes.body: Peach Crescendo, a cross between Peach Rings and Crescendo, is a hybrid strain known for its citrusy tropical flavor, sweet peach exhale, and notes of spice. Peach Crescendo's effects are bar none, it has a full body calming effect that leaves you couch-locked while your mind elevates with clarity and focus. Despite the deep physical relaxation however, your mental energy remains unaffected. It's a popular choice for addressing insomnia, appetite loss, chronic pain, and muscle spasms. Peach Crescendo is great for customers experiencing many types of pain and great for cramps!
